data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4 bedroom/2.5 bath with spacious lot in amenity-rich Timberlands Community. Located in sought-after North Paulding High district convenient to Hiram, Acworth, Kennesaw, and Cartersville. You will feel right at home from the first step into the soaring foyer. Fireside family room with custom built-ins complete w/french doors & leading onto an extra wide front porch perfect for enjoying a book and cup of coffee! Beautifully updated kitchen features custom cabinetry and island, granite countertops, and overlooks eat-in breakfast area. Oversized dining room with tons of natural light. Upstairs boasts a large master suite w/elegant bath featuring a separate tub and shower, double vanities, and owner's closet. Two additional secondary bedrooms each have spacious closets and a large bonus bedroom with many possibilities. All of this sitting atop a full unfinished basement w/single and double door frames and stubbed for bath. Back deck overlooks private, wooded lot and fenced yard. Well-maintained subdivision with reasonable HOA which includes a swimming pool, kids pool, and playground. SHORT SALE APPROVED - SUBJECT TO BANK's FINAL APPROVAL!
